• Lumiverse By Maradox

Hello there! today I'd like to announce that my first map is here!
First of all, this is only the alpha version. the full version will come out soon with 3 Stages and  Boss fights etc!

- Fixes/Updates!

  • Fixed the issue where the white portal always stay active
  • Fixed the "funny" ladder (will be missed.)
  • Re-worked the KZ part on the start (made it shorter)
  • Re-worked the 4th part of the map
  • Fixed the water bug on 5th part
  • Fixed the ending (Zombies don't get Teleported)
